    "title": "Wokovu katika Isaya",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "wokovu katika isaya",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Jina la nabii Isaya linamaanisha <em>Yahweh ni wokovu</em>. Anawahimiza watu kuacha waokozi wa uongo na kumgeukia Mungu ambaye ndiye mwokozi na mlinzi wa kweli pekee. Wokovu unaathiri sehemu zote za maisha, ikijumuisha vipengele vya kimwili na vya kiroho. Kwa mfano, neno <em>wokovu</em> wakati mwingine linaonekana katika kitabu cha Isaya pamoja na <em>Uadilifu</em> kuonyesha hali ya amani ambapo dhuluma, aibu, na maombolezo hayapo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:8\">Isaya 45:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:8\">51:8</a>).</p><p>Isaya mara nyingi hushiriki injili (habari njema kuhusu Yesu) kwamba Bwana atakuja kusaidia watu wake (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:2-Isa4:6\">4:2–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:24-Isa10:34\">10:24–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:9-Isa40:11\">40:9–11</a>). Ingawa Mungu anaahidi adhabu na uhamisho kwa sababu ya makosa ya Waisraeli, Bwana hange waacha. Badala yake, angewaokoa. Nguvu ya Babuloni pamoja na mateso na aibu ya uhamisho vingemalizika. Sura za <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:1-Isa39:8\">1–39</a> zinatabiri ujumbe huu, wakati sura za <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:1-Isa66:24\">40–66</a> zinaueleza wazi.</p><p>Isaya anazungumzia wokovu ambao Mungu ataleta kupitia Yesu Kristo. Anatoa unabii kuhusu &quot;Tawi&quot; kutoka kwa ukoo wa Mfalme Daudi ambaye atakuwa na Roho Mtakatifu na kuleta haki na uadilifu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:5\">11:1–5</a>). Pia anataja mtumishi wa Mungu ambaye atateseka kwa ajili ya dhambi za watu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:13-Isa53:12\">52:13–53:12</a>). Yesu alitimiza unabii wa Isaya na kuwaokoa wanadamu kutoka kwa dhambi na kifo.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1\">Zaburi 27:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:8\">Isaya 49:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:15-Isa59:21\">Isaya 59:15–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">Isaya 61:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:21\">Luka 4:18–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16-John3:17\">Yohana 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:47\">Yohana 12:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9-Rom10:13\">Warumi 10:9–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:18-2Cor5:21\">2 Wakorintho 5:18–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:13\">Tito 2:11–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27-Heb9:28\">Waebrania 9:27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18-1Pet3:21\">1 Petro 3:18–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:10\">Ufunuo 7:9–10</a></p>",
